---
<section class="testimonial-section">
  <div class="container container-narrow gs-test">
    <div class="brutalist-card testimonial-card">
      <blockquote>
        "Perdía 4 clientes por semana por no responder cuando estaba debajo del auto. Hoy, el taller se llena solo."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="author-info">
        <strong>ROBERTO CÁRDENAS</strong>
        <span>DUEÑO SERVITECA R&C</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonial-section {
    background-color: #FEF08A; /* Intense Yellow background */
  }
  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  blockquote {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .author-info strong {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
    border-bottom: 3px solid black;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .author-info span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
